==English==
===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[supino]]'' "to lay on the back"
===Transitive verb===
'''supinate'''

#{{anatomy}}: To twist the [[forearm]] so as to turn the [[palm]] of the [[hand]] away from the body, thereby [[elongate|elongating]] the [[biceps brachii]].

===Antonym===
*[[pronate]]
===Related terms===
*[[supine]]